The ns-3 XGS-PON module has been developed by Dr. Jerome Arokkiam (jerom2005raj@gmail.com) at BT Applied Research in Adastral Park, UK.

This ns-3 XGS-PON module is an upgrade from the previous ns-3 XG-PON module, wich was dveloped by Xiuchao Wu (xw2@cs.ucc.ie) and Jerome Arokkiam (jerome@4c.ucc.ie) during their time at University College Cork (UCC, Ireland), and Pedro Alvarez (pinheirp@tcd.ie) from Trinity College Dublin (TCD, Ireland)
